HEADWORD: Breezeless
<hw>Breeze"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Motionless; destitute of
breezes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A stagnant, <qex>breezeless</qex> air becalms my soul.</q>
<rj><qau>Shenstone.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Breeziness</ent>⟦br⟧
